          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Product Requirements Document \u2014 VidRevamp"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Problem Statement"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Video creators and online business owners shoot hours of footage and publish one video \u2014 leaving 90% of their best content on the cutting room floor. Meanwhile, short-form content on TikTok, Reels, and YouTube Shorts is exploding, but manually repurposing a 45-minute video into 10 clips with captions takes 3\u20135 hours. VidRevamp automates the entire repurposing pipeline: transcription, clip selection, captioning, formatting, and multi-platform scheduling."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Goals"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Turn one long-form video into 10+ platform-ready short clips automatically"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Add captions, intros, and platform-specific formatting without manual editing"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Schedule and distribute across TikTok, Reels, YouTube Shorts, and LinkedIn Video"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Deliver a repurposing report showing which clips got the most traction"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Core Features"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "AI Clip Extractor: identifies the 10 highest-engagement moments from transcript"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Auto-Caption Engine: burned-in captions with brand colors and font"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Platform Formatter: crops and sizes for TikTok (9:16), LinkedIn (1:1), YouTube Shorts"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Hook Scorer: rates each clip's opening 3 seconds for scroll-stop power"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Batch Scheduler: queue 30 days of clips with one click"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
